{"tid":361658,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一億人湧港】中國戰略按排　一小時生活圈　一億人的生活空間　香港","createTime":"2017-08-16T10:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T11:21:36.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b128e6ff6550cf6f40105abb8c3fa571c4ace55","tid":361658,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2009-07-20/hongkong1248076834d1914425.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.singtao.ca%2Fvancouver%2F2009-07-20%2Fhongkong1248076834d1914425.html&d=wUgEeUynGuOXmQDGHl7haTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=4f760f5f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/2009-07-20/hongkong1248076834d1914425.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://news.singtao.ca/vancouver/h003/h87/img200907200400280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.singtao.ca%2Fvancouver%2Fh003%2Fh87%2Fimg200907200400280.jpg&h=c1e048a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n剛剛走訪完珠三角九巿的唐英年，接受本報訪問，解釋今次走訪九巿的背景。他指出，國務院發表的《珠江三角洲地區改革發展規劃綱要》，是將粵港合作提升到國家層次，成為國家的戰略安排。他相信，連同港澳兩地，珠三角區有潛質可以成為全國最具經濟活力的經濟區，「單是廣東省已有9000萬人口，再加上港澳兩地，即共有接近一億人，是相當具規模的經濟容量，可以說是一個接近中型國家的經濟容量&hellip;&hellip;連同香港的生產總值比長三角還要高，我覺得我們是有潛質做全國最具經濟活力的一個區。」"},{"pid":"142af6766a3a666dc1701e58490642b257c180fb","tid":361658,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T10:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20140226/large/26la2p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140226%2Flarge%2F26la2p01.jpg&h=3b6a8f6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b55584c00e30be4d5790020cfc1d823935ab62c","tid":361658,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T11:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}